NaviCharaList.name: Rene
NaviCharaList.description:
History-loving time fairy.
Don't disturb her while reading
or she'll get very scary.

NaviCharaList.name: Astrea
NaviCharaList.description:
A battle-loving time fairy.
She never misses training
unless there's an emergency.

NaviCharaList.name: Maya
NaviCharaList.description:
Carefree fairy of Time.
Her mysterious bag seems
to be full of treasures.
